c: 7
v: 88
t: "Ewﾃｪ desta mezinanﾃｪ ji komalﾃｪ (ﾅ柆ﾂｴeyb) ku xwe qure dikirin (pisyara ﾅ柆ﾂｴeyb aha dane ﾃｻ) gotine: \"ﾅ柆ﾂｴeyb! Bi rastﾃｮ emﾃｪ te ﾃｻ ewanﾃｪ bi te ra bawer kirine, ji gundﾃｪ xwe derxin, ya jﾃｮ hﾃｻnﾃｪ dﾃｮsa werne \"ol\" a me (dﾃｮn).\" (ﾅ柆ﾂｴeyb) gotﾃｮye: \"Heke em ji \"ol\" a we bﾃｪzar bin jﾃｮ (hﾃｻnﾃｪ dﾃｮsa tﾃｪkilﾃｪ me bibin)"